                    <span>It is one of the best book I ever read. The book started in a hotel where Leon's mom works. Leon collects taxi drivers homelands. He meets a taxi driver named Napoleon and they become friends. He always picks Leon up from school and drops him off. His teacher is very weird all they do practically is sew. There is a locked cabinet in the back of the class and Leon takes a peak. They make critters called animles because the teacher does not want them to call them animals because they will get attached to them. This book is very good and I suggest you read it.</span>
                  
